@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v2
    v0 = (wp.cos(tmp) + (wp.cos(v1 + 0.72) * (tmp + 0.77 + v0 + 0.18)))
    v2 = v0
    v1 = 0.24
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.48 * tmp + 0.93)) - 0.79)
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
